records.addlTxt:
Count 1 - OWI 6th offense - No contest plea.  Convicted.
State moves to dismiss and read in Count 2, PAC - 6th offense.  Motion granted.
Sentence is withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for three (3) years.  Conditions of probation:
1) Nine (9) months Manitowoc County Jail, Huber law, commencing immediately;
2) $1,500.00 fine plus costs, total $2,958.00;
3) AODA assessment and follow through counseling; 
4) Submit a DNA sample if one not already furnished; 
5) Maintain absolute sobriety; and
6) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
In addition, the Court revokes the defendant's driving privileges for a period of thirty-six (36) months.  Ignitition interlock for period of revocation.
Minutes.
